window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Lily Ivory hopes for a normal life when she opens Aunt Cora's Closet. With her magical knack for vintage fashion - she can sense vibrations of the past from clothing and jewelry - her store becomes a big hit. But when a client is murdered and children start disappearing from the Bay Area, Lily may be the only one who can unravel the crime. </p> <p>She tries to keep her identity a secret while investigating, but it's not easy - especially under the spells of sexy \"mythbuster\" Max Carmichael and powerful witch Aidan Rhodes. Will Lily's witchy ways be forced out of the closet?</p>"; 
